  hjb.http.cmd.ParameterMapDecoder

Method Detail

decode

public Map decode(Map parameterMap)
Decodes the values in parameterMap.

It assumes that

  • Only the first element of the array value (the input map's values are String arrays) is relevant, (because the other value must have been sent by mistake!)
  • The value will be encoded, and may require decoding using a TypedValueCodec
  • Only the value of the parameters returned by getCompulsoryDecodings() are decoded. The others as passed through as-is.

Parameters:
parameterMap - a Map like that returned by ServletRequest.getParameterMap()
Returns:
an unmodifiable Map containing the values decoded from parameterMap
